{"tid":1442937,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Versace 都鼓吹港獨","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:05:24.000Z","uid":184146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b91ca4462f1323964db186cd455e2d70fb6e0053","tid":1442937,"uid":184146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"【楊冪於凌晨向Versace解除】疑因鼓吹港獨？<br />\n<br />\n今年六月才宣布為Versace中國首位代言人的楊冪，竟然於今天凌晨兩點時忽然發表一篇聲明，向品牌發出了解除協議！<br />\n<br />\n聲明稿上寫出因為發現了 Versace 在網上發售的一件tee恤，涉及損害中國國家主權及領土完整，原來tee恤上列出世界各地多個城市及其所屬國家，並以「城市－國家」的方式印上，如「London-UK」、「Beijing-CHINA」等。但香港和澳門，卻也是「Hong Kong-HONG KONG」和「Macau-MACAO」，而非「Hong Kong-CHINA」或「Macau-CHINA」。疑似表示香港及澳門為獨立國家非中國領土，涉及政治敏感話題，讓中國人民無法接受。<br />\n<br />\n(Source: FashionWeek Weibo)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAyZfLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAyZfLk.png&h=39330d96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWsZ0b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWsZ0b1.png&h=a8d2fe9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mfXMR3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mfXMR3.png&h=0b584d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想買返件"},{"pid":"4e11217086f0ad2159390f4ad0f3b269d9cdb75b","tid":1442937,"uid":181035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"好少著白T 但都想買返件"},{"pid":"fee35a5fccfae17788dcaac3d50586ecd1bc1cf9","tid":1442937,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>等一下</strong></span></span>"}]}